WEBVTT

00:13:28.628 --> 00:13:30.218
Ne grizite si nohtov.

00:13:30.362 --> 00:13:32.388
Ne brišite si nosu v hrbet roke.

00:13:32.388 --> 00:13:34.711
No, tega nikakor ne počnite, 
ker je ogabno.

00:13:34.711 --> 00:13:35.730
(smeh)

00:13:36.270 --> 00:13:38.102
Ne nosite obraznih mask.

00:13:38.789 --> 00:13:41.639
Obrazne maske so za bolne ljudi in
zdravstvene delavce.

00:13:41.639 --> 00:13:45.787
Če ste bolani, vaša maska zadrži
vse kašljanje in kihanje

00:13:45.787 --> 00:13:47.493
in zaščiti ljudi okoli vas.

00:13:47.962 --> 00:13:49.634
Če ste zdravstveni delavec,

00:13:49.634 --> 00:13:52.370
je obrazna maska eno izmed orodij,

00:13:52.370 --> 00:13:54.309
ki se imenuje zaščitna oprema

00:13:54.309 --> 00:13:57.140
in ki jo nosite, da lahko nudite 
pacientom pomoč

00:13:57.140 --> 00:13:58.504
in ne lastne bolezni.

00:13:58.594 --> 00:14:02.272
Če ste normalno zdrava oseba,
bo nošenje obrazne maske